@*ABOUT US*@
<div id="AboutUs" class="container pt-5">
    <div class="test"></div>
    <h1 class="pt-5 pb-3"> &nbsp About Us</h1>
    <img class="col-8 col-lg-5 mr-5 pb-3" src="~/images/GroupPhoto.jpg" />
    <p class="col-8" id="AboutUs-text">
        <b>xShapes</b> is a final year project by a team of 3 Republic polytechnic students with a vision.
        Our aim is to develop an <b>object detection system</b> that can detect shapes to <b>help with inventory management. </b>
        Along with Web and Mobile application to monitor inventory level in <b>real time</b> anywhere and anytime!
    </p>
</div>

@*FEATURES*@
<div id="Features" class="container pt-5">
    
    <div class="test"></div>
    <h1 class=" pt-5 pb-3">Features</h1>
</div>
<div class="container pt-2 pb-5">

    @*Object Detection*@
    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div id="carouselObjectControls" class="carousel slide col-md-6 col-10 " data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#carouselObjectIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselObjectIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselObjectIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/detection.jpg" alt="First slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/wholeproject.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/physical model.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselObjectControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselObjectControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 col-8">
            <h2 class=" pb-3 pt-5   ">Object Detection</h2>
            <p id="Feature1-text">
                Our system currently can detect 6 shapes: <b>Square, Circle, Triangle, Heart, Beaker and Fire. </b>
                Counting the number of shapes, and determining the number of item present. 
                We are able to <b>train a diversity of shapes</b> that is customized to your needs. 
                Basically anything that is unique for instance, QR code or even a bar code. 

            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

